SOUTH ATLANTIC.
TRISTAN DA CUNHA TO SOUTH AFRICA.
DNC 01.
S/V WAY TO BRISBANE, WHITE HULL, ONE PERSON ON BOARD,
OVERDUE TRISTAN DA CUNHA (37-07S 012-17W)
TO CAPE TOWN (33-54S 018-26E).
VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT,
ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO MRCC CAPE TOWN OR CAPE TOWN RADIO.
